ntry to\\n./forge/docs/architecture.md:338:  `strategies/predefined_strategies.json` referencing existing agent +\\n./forge/docs/functional-spec.md:50:| **Predefined strategy** | Named, fully parameterized combination of agent + workflow strategy + prompts + parameters in [strategies/predefined_strategies.json](../strategies/predefined_strategies.json). Selected via `--strategy-name`. |\\n./forge/docs/functional-spec.md:51:| **Post-generation intervention** | Recovery step a strategy invokes when the post-iteration `./gradlew test` still fails. Pluggable via the `PostGenerationIntervention` registry. Configured per predefined strategy (`post-generation-intervention.name`). Concrete implementations: `noop`, `codex_then_pi` (default), `native_trace_collect`. See [workflow-strategies.md §5](workflow-strategies.md#5-post-generation-interventions). |\\n./forge/docs/functional-spec.md:73:- `--strategy-name <name>` — selects an entry from `predefined_strategies.json`.\\n./forge/docs/functional-spec.md:81:Each entry in `strategies/predefined_strategies.json` must provide:\\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:7:> their predefined-strategy entry; this document defines the underlying\\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:62:in their predefined-strategy entry; nothing else changes inside the\\n./forge/docs/native-metadata-exploration.md:393:`native_trace_collect` in their `predefined_strategies.json` entry. The\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:10:[`predefined_strategies.json`](../strategies/predefined_strategies.json)) and\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:37:        Predef[(\\\"predefined_strategies.json<br/>agent + model + prompts + params\\\")]\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:105:  `__init__` raises if the strategy config from `predefined_strategies.json`\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:226:[`predefined_strategies.json`](../strategies/predefined_strategies.json)\\n./forge/docs/workflow-strategies.md:250:predefined-strategy entry; today's